*''Sorry Welcome.'' Oakland, CA: TBW, 2013. Subscription Series #4, Book #2. Edition of 1500. Sanguinetti, [[Christian Patterson]], [[Raymond Meeks]] and [[Wolfgang Tillmans]] each had one book in a set of four.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tbwbooks.com/books/Subscription-Series-4 |accessdate=5 September 2015 |publisher=TBW Books |title=Subscription Series 4 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021033515/http://www.tbwbooks.com/books/Subscription-Series-4 |archivedate=21 October 2015 |df= }}</ref>
